Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:02.92,TEXT CN UP,,0,0,0,,Our sound is not of light, nor is it of the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:08.01,TEXT CN UP,,0,0,0,,Surrender yourself; this night is yours to make
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:13.86,TEXT CN UP,,0,0,0,,Come on, swear it, shout it - loud and clear "EMS"
